description: Re-opening the Manx border will complete the process, Chief Minister Howard Quayle tells Tynwald.
title: Coronavirus Isle of Man: Lockdown 'to be eased in six phases'
title_page: Coronavirus Isle of Man: Lockdown 'to be eased in six phases' - BBC News
maintext: A decision on when the second phase might be rolled out will be made "on or around" 8 May - two weeks after the implementation of phase one.
